  <h1>Jam Lab Support</h1>

  <p>
    Need help with Jam Lab, want to report a bug, or have feedback about the app?
    You can contact support by email:
  </p>

  <p>
    <strong>Email:</strong>
    <a href="mailto:[YOUR_SUPPORT_EMAIL]">amazedbrane@gmail.com</a>
  </p>

  <h2>What to include in your message</h2>

  <p>
    To help us understand the issue, please include:
  </p>

  <ul>
    <li>the device you are using, such as iPhone or iPad,</li>
    <li>your iOS or iPadOS version,</li>
    <li>the Jam Lab app version,</li>
    <li>a short description of what happened,</li>
    <li>the steps to reproduce the issue, if possible.</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>Privacy</h2>

  <p>
    You can read the Jam Lab Privacy Policy here:
    <a href="../privacy/">Privacy Policy</a>.
  </p>

  <h2>Legal Notice</h2>

  <p>
    You can read the Jam Lab Legal Notice here:
    <a href="../legalNotice/">Legal Notice</a>.
  </p>

  <hr>

